{
  "id": "adv_event_2601_01_05_02",
  "title": "全世界に\n生配信！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、終わった終わった\nったく、あんた達の顔を見ながら年越しとかさぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8145070425,
      "endTime": 8.4486339918,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6850.9801864
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 8.6486338964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、{user}さんからメール",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6486338964,
      "endTime": 10.793212703,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1818.0279174000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "チャンネルの登録者数、初動で三十万だってさ\nこれって、いい数字なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5668943436,
      "endTime": 18.1600914986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3734249463
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "国内基準なら、まあまあかな\nでもまだkanaのチャンネルには、全然負けるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3734249463,
      "endTime": 25.2785041204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.4651709587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、kanaのチャンネルは海外からも見られてるし\nそうなると、数字が桁から違うからさ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4651709587,
      "endTime": 34.351678755900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、とにかくこれで肩の荷が下りたわ\n正月は、やっとゆっくり休めそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5650121083,
      "endTime": 41.139819561500005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 34.5650121083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブとチャンネルの準備で、全然休む暇なかったしね\nもう正月はゴロゴロする、全力でゴロゴロしてやるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3531530093,
      "endTime": 51.4448085498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3531530093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "貴方はまず、今からでも大掃除をしなさい\nさて……それじゃあ、私は先に帰らせてもらうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6514750829,
      "endTime": 60.438436447499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 60.631769533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "それと……儀礼として、一応言っておくけれど\n二人とも、あけましておめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.631769533,
      "endTime": 68.92573801969999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9201.565559599992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1190713912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。あけましておめでとう\n……あれ？　なんで私の部屋のこと知ってるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1190713912,
      "endTime": 78.5052618056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8666692844
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――1月1日、午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3785940837,
      "endTime": 80.47859408369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5452651215
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 80.5785874716
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 80.7000016006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ただの街中の神社だと思ってたけど\nさすがに元旦ともなると、そこそこ人がいるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3785874716,
      "endTime": 90.5950951925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.7817617448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、お参りだけしてさっさと帰ろ……\n…………げ。なんでいるのよ、あんた達",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7817617448,
      "endTime": 99.1333349339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1756624252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……初詣で、まさか煩悩の権化に出くわすなんて\n…………え？　あんた『達』って、どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8000016006,
      "endTime": 111.23759315330001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.3014973867
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3411803912
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 111.3411803912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "うげ……やっと休み取ったのに、あんた達に会うとか\nもうこれって労災じゃない？　申請下りない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2665954303,
      "endTime": 121.0150083255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.1332599353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……事務所の近くの神社に来たのが間違いだったわ\n帰省か、もう少し遠出すれば良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2150081348,
      "endTime": 130.6039935779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.2150081348
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.7906601301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "今年こそ、ブランドが軌道に乗りますように\nがっぽがっぽ儲けて、事業資金が潤沢になりますように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7906601301,
      "endTime": 139.8582334868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1333420546
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.058233296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "今度こそ、VENUSグランプリで優勝して\nトップアイドルの座に就けますように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.058233296,
      "endTime": 145.64326747570001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8299343141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "……さてと、お参りもしたし……あ、絵馬みっけ\nせっかくだし、何か書いていこうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8299343141,
      "endTime": 154.4899339708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.6966005994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "そう。お好きに\n……それと、チャンネルの朝の反応も見てきたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.6966005994,
      "endTime": 161.89660069480001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム実況は、やはりコメントが格段に多いわね\n「自分も好きなゲームをやってくれて嬉しかった」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0966008855,
      "endTime": 169.5966006948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.0966008855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "「ガチでゲーム楽しんでるのが伝わって良かった」\n「これでも友情が壊れないのが凄い」……ですって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
